    participant U as User (REST Client)
    participant A as FastAPI Server
    participant Q as Job Queue
    participant W as Worker Manager
    participant E as Windows Executor
    participant D as Docker Engine (Windows)
    participant S as SQLite DB

    U->>A: POST /build {repo, project, cmd}
    A->>S: Create BuildRecord (QUEUED)
    A->>Q: Push(build_id)
    A-->>U: 202 Accepted {build_id}

    W->>Q: Pop()
    W->>S: Update Status (CLONING)
    W->>E: run_build()
    E->>E: Clone Repository
    W->>S: Update Status (RUNNING)
    E->>D: Run Container (Mount Source)
    D->>D: MSBuild / Publish
    D-->>E: Stream Logs
    E-->>W: log_callback(line)
    W->>S: Persist LogRecord
    D-->>E: Exit(0)
    E->>E: Zip Artifacts
    W->>S: Update Status (SUCCESS)
    W->>S: Set artifact_path

    U->>A: GET /build/{id}/logs
    A->>S: Query Logs
    A-->>U: [Log lines...]

    U->>A: GET /build/{id}/artifact
    A->>S: Get artifact_path
    A-->>U: Download zip
